<paragraph blockId="30.[151,1437,152,935]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Sexual dimorphism moderately manifested, in males apex of mid tibiae with distinct black spine and apex of last ventrite deeply emarginate; in females apex of mid tibiae with minute black spine and apex of last ventrite truncate or shallowly emarginate.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="30.[151,1437,152,935]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,406,621,647]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Immature stages.</emphasis>
Larva was described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Risbec, J." box="[686,837,621,647]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" pagination="1 - 13" refId="ref49731" refString="Risbec, J. (1934) Le cocotier en Nouvelle-Caledonie. L'Agronomie Coloniale, 23 (199), 1 - 13." type="journal article" year="1934">Risbec (1934</bibRefCitation>
